# 召喚位置決定
    summon area_effect_cloud ^-16 ^0.1 ^15 {Tags:["AK.IceCrepation.Pos","AK.IceCrepation.Pos.A"],Duration:70}
    summon area_effect_cloud ^-8 ^0.1 ^19 {Tags:["AK.IceCrepation.Pos","AK.IceCrepation.Pos.A"],Duration:70}
